{
  "stem": "214.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So the German head of the office, when he heard her tell somebody who wants to apply, free willing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He called me to his desk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And first he asked me, why do you want to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I said, I am an orphan, and I was smuggling till now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the last times didn't work anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I decided I really have to work for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he gives me, you know, glorious picture of how a will live in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I will go to a beautiful city called Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I will-- he said I would be working in a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I would have enough food to eat, and so forth, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that really-- and call somebody and ask him to fill out my papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I had my name, Anna Wojcik, I had all those things prepared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I couldn't find it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I hid it somewhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they didn't even ask me and give me all the document.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then the train ticket-- I have to be at 6 o'clock in the morning, the following day, at the station to go to [NON-ENGLISH,] no, to go to Lublin, which was sort of a transit place where I'm going to go through medical examination.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And since I have already a place where to go, to Stuttgart, I won't even have to wait, because they were usually sending out contingents of 100.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I won't even have to wait, which was important to me, to be among 100 Poles, waiting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I will be there, you know, in two, three days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And that's really what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And when I came to Stuttgart, and I went to the [NON-ENGLISH], so they gave me an assignment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There came a nun.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
